{"word":"κραυγάζω","slug":"κραυγάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κραυγάζω</b></el> <el>(κραυγάζω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κραυγή'><el>κραυγή</el></a>\n<p/><i>to bay</i>, of dogs, Poeta <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; of men, <i>to cry aloud, scream</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}